38, 160.1872, 161.9083, 161.4974, 161.5836, 162.3028, 162.1474, 162.261, 162.1752, 161.6872, 162.0963, 163.5098, 163.7858, 162.6348, 161.9115, 161.4982, 161.9665, 161.8475, 161.6922, 161.5169, 161.1469, 161.4456, 161.7834, 161.3861, 161.6949, 162.6029, 162.1889, 161.9093, 161.2145, 162.7838, 161.7137, 161.3218, 160.5298, 161.5005, 162.0264, 162.4623, 162.7563, 161.0618, 160.3651, 159.6873, 159.059, 158.6132, 159.581, 159.8866, 160.1558, 160.5975, 160.1999, 160.68, 161.1363, 160.6792, 160.6703, 160.8634, 160.8797, 160.9745, 161.9126, 162.5022, 161.2289, 160.83, 160.7387, 160.9408, 161.881, 161.2437, 162.2376, 162.3846, 161.9722, 162.3212, 163.1817, 162.6265, 163.4181, 164.2653, 164.8305, 165.267, 164.9467, 165.4105, 166.1951, 166.7552, 166.8986, 166.7904, 167.2517, 168.0804, 169.6081, 168.7462, 168.8307, 167.3123, 166.8107, 166.8536, 166.8805, 166.821, 166.7912, 167.541, 169.0982, 169.7183, 168.5045, 169.2397, 170.4035, 169.9153, 170.7465, 171.5133, 170.9259, 170.3924, 170.3848, 170.9032, 171.466, 173.299, 172.9526, 171.8112, 172.5801, 173.5859, 170.6088, 168.4483, 169.358, 169.4537, 168.163, 168.3404, 168.159, 167.9161, 167.8755, 167.4699, 168.2166, 167.9363, 167.8469, 167.7276, 167.2632, 166.6615, 166.0263, 165.496, 167.0246, 170.3182, 172.4301, 168.7916, 173.5524, 174.2063, 174.0016, 175.5687, 175.7441, 177.8074, 178.022, 177.4936, 176.4513, 176.7129, 175.1932, 176.9286, 177.798, 176.4169, 176.6494, 174.9216, 176.931, 176.893, 177.4302, 174.0356, 174.6881, 174.2094, 174.0511, 173.533, 173.3352, 173.6893, 172.5823, 174.2022, 174.2433, 175.2087, 174.703, 174.2357, 174.28, 175.3944, 176.1389, 176.6981, 176.5191, 176.1843, 176.3339, 177.523, 177.3172, 178.1587, 176.679, 175.735, 176.4069, 176.6182, 176.9559, 176.3209, 175.6807, 176.2149, 174.7021, 174.7001, 175.6855, 176.659, 177.6923, 177.6034, 177.2803, 177.3501, 177.5444, 177.1365, 177.3605, 176.7457, 175.9437, 176.664, 177.5624, 177.7971, 177.1202, 176.1364, 176.4128, 175.0165, 174.9558, 174.583, 173.5701, 173.1825, 173.91, 173.8538, 174.4388, 175.1588, 173.1265], "summary_html": "<h1>20240101_paper_Forecasting the dail</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>首篇用经济理论模型（货币模型 + 理性预期现值框架）预测主要货币对日频汇率的研究。核心是 Mark(1995)/Chinn-Meese(1995) 误差修正预测模型：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">s_{t+1}-s_t = \\alpha_1 + \\beta_1 d_t^{(h)} + \\epsilon_{t+1}</div>\n<p><span class=\"math-tex\">s_t</span> 为即期汇率对数，<span class=\"math-tex\">d_t^{(h)}</span> 为合成远期汇率 <span class=\"math-tex\">D_t^{(h)}=S_t(1+i_t)/(1+i^*_t)</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">d_t=\\log D_t</span>。作者证明长期限(3/5/10年)合成远期可近似基本面均衡与即期的缺口 <span class=\"math-tex\">(f_t-s_t)</span>。递归估参，交易规则：预测 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat s_{t+k}&lt;d_t</span> 买入、否则卖出；基准为远期本身(carry trade)与随机游走。结果在1天到5年所有期限显著优于随机游走，年化超额 3-4%。</p>\n<h3>CTA 迁移</h3>\n<p>合成远期−即期缺口本质由利差/carry 驱动。商品类比为展期收益率 ry(真实近远月年化价差)与基差 basis(现货−期货)——正是 FX 利差缺口的商品对应物。复现期曾测试 carry / 滞后 basis / 慢速 carry-EMA 三个误差修正项及其等权组合(Combined)，但<strong>入库的实盘变体 <code>ecm_basis_h3</code>(meta 名 <code>ecm_basis_h3_raw</code>)已收敛到单一基差形态</strong>，无组合。生产 <code>strategy_final.py</code> 的实际信号构造(<strong>逐品种时序因子，非截面</strong>)：</p>\n<ul><li><strong>误差修正项 d_t = basis.shift(1)</strong>(滞后 1 日防建库前视)。</li>\n<li><strong>因果滚动 OLS(窗口 252)</strong>：用滞后 1 日的已实现次日对数收益 <code>fwd_ret.shift(1)</code> 对滞后 <code>d_{t-1}</code> 回归估出 <span class=\"math-tex\">(a_t,b_t)</span>(闭式滚动矩，min_periods=126)，再代入<strong>当期可观测的</strong> <span class=\"math-tex\">d_t</span> 得预测 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat s_{t+1|t}=a_t+b_t d_t</span>。</li>\n<li><strong>EMA(span=3)轻平滑</strong>预测以降换手 → <strong>时序 z-score(窗口 63)并 clip 到 [−3,3]</strong> 作为连续幅度 → <strong>vol-target(0.15, 杠杆 2.0, 波动窗 20)</strong> 缩放 → <strong>每 3 日再平衡持有</strong>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>方向上预测涨则做多、跌则做空，对应原文\"预测高于即期则买入\"。<strong>关键发现</strong>：单一 basis EC 项即最优(Sharpe ≈ 0.98)，carry-EMA 与组合变体均次于它；这是<strong>时序因子</strong>(ts-IC≈0.017、ts-ICIR 0.76、ts-IC&gt;0 占 82%)，靠单品种时序择时而非截面分散；与因子库最大相关 0.38(marginal，非冗余)。<strong>防前视</strong>：basis 已 shift(1)；OLS 用滞后 y,x 估参、仅代入当期 d_t；z-score/EMA/vol 滚动窗均后视；rebalance_hold 只前向持有(与 audit 一致)。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.93</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-10.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.12</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3434</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.14</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.23 / 1.07</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.23</td><td>0.38</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.07</span></td><td>1.19</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.35</span></td><td>0.95</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.42</span></td><td>0.07</td><td>0.72</td><td>1.69</td><td>1.55</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.89</span></td><td>1.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 3 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 3 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3436</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>82.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>41.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>因果滚动 OLS(用滞后 y,x 估参再代入当期 <span class=\"math-tex\">d_t</span> 防前视)：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\hat b_t=\\frac{Cov_{[t-W,t-1]}(s_{\\tau+1}-s_\\tau,\\,d_{\\tau-1})}{Var_{[t-W,t-1]}(d_{\\tau-1})},\\quad \\hat a_t=\\bar y-\\hat b_t\\bar x,\\quad \\hat s_{t+1|t}=\\hat a_t+\\hat b_t d_t,\\ W=252</div>\n<p>实盘变体仅用 basis 单项(<span class=\"math-tex\">d_t=</span> basis<span class=\"math-tex\">_{t-1}</span>)，无组合(组合 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat s^{comb}=\\frac13(\\hat s^{carry}+\\hat s^{basis}+\\hat s^{ryema})</span> 为复现期对照，未入库)。 仓位(连续)：<span class=\"math-tex\">z=\\text{clip}(zscore_{63}(EMA_3(\\hat s_{basis})),\\,-3,3)</span>，vol-target 15%(波动窗 20、杠杆 2.0)后每 3 天再平衡。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li>R1(0.91)：实现误差修正预测模型(三 EC 项 carry/basis/carry-EMA + 组合预测，连续与符号变体)。ecm_basis_raw 0.91 居首，半样本稳定(1.18/1.43)。诊断：日换手 7.79、累计手续费 7.1 严重侵蚀——EC 符号日内频繁翻转。</li>\n<li>R2(0.86)：span=10 重平滑 + IC gate + 长 hold。换手降到 1.18，但过度稀释毛信号，毛 Sharpe 同步下滑，无 gate 的 ecm_combined_sgn_raw 反成最优。结论：gate 削弱了稳健的毛 edge。</li>\n<li>R3(0.979,通过)：轻平滑 span=3 保留 edge，去 gate，网格 hold∈{3,5}。ecm_basis_h3_raw 0.979，换手回到 4.81 折中区，ts_ICIR 0.76、ts_IC&gt;0 82%，decision=skip。关键转折：R2 验证 gate+重平滑会杀毛信号，R3 用轻平滑在换手与 edge 间找最优平衡，较 R1 净提升约 7%。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li>数据频率：日频(comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet)。</li>\n<li>品种范围：全商品期货主力连续(约 50-58 个)，无全局黑名单。</li>\n<li>核心字段：ry、basis(已 shift(1) 防建库前视)、ryminusema63。</li>\n<li>已知局限：(1) 原文用 GBP/USD 单货币对+利率曲线，商品迁移用 carry/basis 作合成远期缺口类比，非完全等价；(2) 换手偏高(4.81)，对成本敏感；(3) 2018/2021/2025 较弱；(4) 最大回撤较深(-59%)，vol-target 后绝对杠杆偏高，实盘需叠加组合层风控。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>EC_COL</code></td><td><code>&quot;basis&quot;</code></td><td>error-correction term (basis spread)</td></tr><tr><td><code>OLS_WIN</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>causal rolling OLS window</td></tr><tr><td><code>EMA_SPAN</code></td><td><code>3</code></td><td>forecast smoothing</td></tr><tr><td><code>Z_WIN</code></td><td><code>63</code></td><td>ts z-score window for magnitude</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9997</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.35s</li>\n</ul>"}